{"type":"entity","name":"Dify_Backend","entityType":"Component","observations":["Python Flask 应用，遵循领域驱动设计","包管理: uv run --project api","测试框架: pytest（Arrange-Act-Assert）","代码规范: Ruff 格式化 + ruff linting","ORM: SQLAlchemy（继承 models.base.TypeBase）","异步任务: Celery + Redis Broker","架构: 控制器 → 服务 → 核心/领域 分层架构","隶属 Dify_Platform，作为 PKIA 的底层 API 基础设施"]}
{"type":"entity","name":"Dify_Frontend","entityType":"Component","observations":["框架: Next.js + TypeScript + React","包管理: pnpm（工作空间根目录）","测试框架: Vitest + React Testing Library","代码规范: ESLint（pnpm lint:fix）+ pnpm type-check","覆盖组件: 仅使用 @langgenius/dify-ui/* 覆盖原语","国际化: 所有用户可见字符串放入 web/i18n/en-US/","隶属 Dify_Platform，作为 PKIA 的底层前端基础设施"]}
{"type":"entity","name":"Three_Tier_Memory_System","entityType":"Architecture","observations":["L1 宪法层 (.clinerules): 智能体潜意识与绝对行为边界","L2 图谱层 (cline-memory.json via MCP): Workspace Memory","L3 进度层 (PROGRESS.md): 短期工作记忆与大脑草稿本","强制记忆流转协议 (Bouncer Protocol): 任务结束时必须执行 payload → 门禁脚本 → 验证销毁","目标: 对抗注意力稀释 (Attention Drift) 与幻觉","作为 PKIA 项目的状态管理基础设施","L1 宪法层 (.clinerules): 已更新为 PKIA 核心定位","L2 图谱层 (cline-memory.json via MCP): Workspace Memory","L3 进度层 (PROGRESS.md): PKIA 研发短期工作记忆"]}
{"type":"entity","name":"Memory_Bouncer_Script","entityType":"Script","observations":["位于 utils/memory_bouncer.py","功能: 校验 memory_payload JSON、追加 L2 图谱增量、替换 L3 进度锚点、自动 Git 操作","状态: 尚未创建，需在后续任务中补齐","Exit Code 0 表示成功"]}
